{"tid":927416,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「巴拿馬文件」揭習家族避稅隱瞞資產","createTime":"2018-12-04T06:55:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-04T09:55:23.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"03e8d44e2dbbac02e8257ec9f2adfd6ac99c1d3c","tid":927416,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T06:55:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181204/20560858\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181204%2F20560858&d=AtWwe%2FdLOZlZPdCPsK%2F9a%2FjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=f5debc0a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181204%2F20560858&h=1a146d35\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181204/20560858</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年12月04日 <br />\n<br />\n「巴拿馬文件」揭習家族避稅隱瞞資產<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181204/large/a1403a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181204%2Flarge%2Fa1403a.gif&h=75aeb44a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n習近平拉美之行延續銀彈政策，簽巨額協議增加影響力。美聯社<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n巴拿馬對習近平來說，也是一個「傷心之地」。它不僅擁有連接太平洋和大西洋的運河，亦因「巴拿馬文件」聞名於世。國際調查記者同盟（ICIJ）2016年4月取得巴拿馬一家律師行文件，揭示國際權貴利用該國避稅隱藏海外資產，包括習近平姐夫鄧家貴等，在巴拿馬註冊公司，至少八名中共現任或離任政要的家人親屬，在此設離岸企業隱瞞財富。<br />\n<br />\n文件披露，習近平家族、前總理李鵬女兒李小琳、全國政協前主席賈慶林外孫女李紫丹等都有開離岸公司。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n被揭設離岸空殼公司<br />\n<br />\n習的姊姊齊橋橋（隨母姓）丈夫鄧家貴，2009年在英屬群島成立兩間空殼公司，鄧是公司唯一董事與股東，註冊地報稱是香港灣仔駱克大廈一單位。不過在習2012年11月任中共總書記之前，公司已停止運作。<br />\n<br />\n習近平姐夫醜聞曝光後，中國外交部發言人曾稱「對於這種捕風捉影的東西（巴拿馬文件），我們不作評論」。同年4月18日習在中共一個內部會議上，鄭重要求「規範領導幹部配偶、子女及其配偶經商辦企業行為」，並稱率先在上海「試點」，接着要在北京、廣東、重慶、新疆推廣，要求全黨「從嚴規範、率先規範、以上率下」。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》記者  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n華擬巴拿馬運河旁建使館　美施壓阻止<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n華斥672億貨幣互換協議助阿根廷"},{"pid":"5afc3fc8bf1df41fb94fd2c11494ea0851d2c756","tid":927416,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T07:56:14.000Z","msg":"原來有 d   交情架 bor, 佢2個 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f1aaa070d421dcbb350fbfbf11d94688a7f74c3","tid":927416,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5afc3fc8bf1df41fb94fd2c11494ea0851d2c756","tid":927416,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T07:56:14.000Z","msg":"原來有 d   交情架 bor, 佢2個 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T09:55:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2017-06-13/656/20170613002817.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2017-06-13%2F656%2F20170613002817.jpg&h=0cd399cd&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}